6장 연습문제 6

서울시립대학교 통계학과

4/29/2021

자료 읽기

prob66 <- read.csv("problem66.txt", header=TRUE, sep="")
prob66$subject  <- factor(prob66$subject)
prob66$drug <- factor(prob66$drug)
prob66$timeF <- factor(prob66$time)

prob66N <- prob66 %>% filter(drug == "N")
prob66P <- prob66 %>% filter(drug == "P")

head(prob66)
##   subject drug time dist timeF
## 1       1    N    0  190     0
## 2       2    N    0   98     0
## 3       3    N    0  155     0
## 4       4    N    0  245     0
## 5       5    N    0  182     0
## 6       6    N    0  140     0

개체별 그림

ggplot(prob66N, aes(x=time, y=dist)) +
     geom_point(size=0.5) +
     stat_smooth(method = "lm",se=F,size=0.5)+
     facet_wrap('subject', labeller = label_both)+ 
     theme_bw() +
     labs(title =  "Novafyline")
## `geom_smooth()` using formula 'y ~ x'

ggplot(prob66P, aes(x=time, y=dist)) +
     geom_point(size=0.5) +
     stat_smooth(method = "lm",se=F,size=0.5)+
     facet_wrap('subject', labeller = label_both)+ 
     theme_bw() + 
     labs(title ="Placebo")
## `geom_smooth()` using formula 'y ~ x'

ggplot(prob66, aes(x=time, y=dist, color = drug) )+
  geom_line(aes(group = subject))

시간별 평균 그림

prob66 %>% 
  ggplot(aes(time, dist, color=drug, fill=drug))  + 
  stat_summary(fun.data = mean_se, alpha=1, position=position_dodge(width=.5)) +
  stat_summary(fun = mean, geom="line", position=position_dodge(width=.5))

혼합모형 분석
